file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: Sample with query parameter without collectionFormat
  version: "1.0"
paths:
  /system/group_membership:
    get:
      summary: Invoke the foo.
      operationId: getFoo
      parameters:
        - name: users
          in: query
          description: foo
          required: true
          style: form
          explode: false
          schema:
            type: array
            items:
              type: string
      responses:
        "202":
          description: foo
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  description:
                    type: string
                    description: Details about the accepted request.
servers:
  - url: https://haible.de/bruno/ibm
